    "heading": "controlbilling",
    "content": "Billing endpoints require `billing_enabled=True` on your org. If billing is not yet enabled, these calls raise `BillingNotEnabledError`. Use `control.interest.express(...)` to join the waitlist."
  }, {
    "heading": "controlkeys",
    "content": "API key management. &#x2A;*Requires `org_role == \"org:admin\"`** — plain API keys will receive `AuthorizationError`."
  }, {
