  }, {
    "heading": "async-variant",
    "content": "`AsyncMemsyControlClient` is the async counterpart. Every method is identical but returns a coroutine."
  }, {
    "heading": "async-variant",
    "content": "Sub-resources (`control.usage`, `control.billing`, `control.keys`, `control.events`, `control.interest`) are all available with `await` equivalents."
