  "contents": [{
    "heading": undefined,
    "content": "Memsy splits your data into two distinct things: **events** (raw input) and **memories** (extracted, searchable output)."
  }, {
    "heading": "events-the-raw-input",
    "content": "An **event** is an immutable record of something that happened in your application. You send events to Memsy; you never edit them after the fact."
  }, {
    "heading": "events-the-raw-input",
    "content": "In the SDK an event is an `EventPayload`:"
